TI  - Advancing justice after climate disaster in the Philippines.
T2  - Farming Matters
M3  - Journal article
AB  - On Sicogon Island in the Philippines, farmers and fisher folk were displaced from their land and livelihoods after the Typhoon Yolanda. Opportunistic land grabbing after a climate disaster is yet another example in which those least responsible for climate change suffer its gravest consequences.
